        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks for parcel of shoots with several interesting cases of "bud-variation".</p>
            <p>Asks for information about roses.</p>
            <p>Strange that great changes in peaches are less rare than slight ones and no case seems recorded of new apples or pears or apricots by "bud-variation". "How ignorant we are!"</p>
        </abstract>
